# No environment variables are required to run this project locally.
# The dashboard is fully client-side and uses in-memory mock data.
#
# When you are ready to connect your own backend, you can add variables here, e.g.:
# VITE_API_BASE_URL=https://your-api.example.com/api
#
# Then reference them in your code as: import.meta.env.VITE_API_BASE_URL
